<head>
	<script src="http://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.4/jquery.min.js" type="text/javascript"></script> 
	<script src="jquery.localscroll.js" type="text/javascript"></script> 
	<script src="jquery.scrollTo.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
	<script type="text/javascript">
		$(document).ready(function() {
		   $('#nav').localScroll({ duration: 3000});
		});
	</script>
</head>

<div class="header">
	<div class="home-menu pure-menu pure-menu-open pure-menu-horizontal pure-menu-fixed">
		<a class="pure-menu-heading" href>StoryTime</a>
		<ul id="nav">
			<li><a href="#">Home</a></li>
			<li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
			<li><a href="#contact">Contact Us</a></li>
		</ul>
	</div>
</div>
<center>
	<div class="splash-container">
		<div class="splash">
			<div class="splash-head">
				<h1>StoryTime</h1>
				<h2>Bedtime stories by text.</h2>
			</div>
				<div class="row">
				    <%= form_for(@user, class: "pure-form") do |f| %>

				      <%= f.telephone_field :phone_number, :placeholder => "Cell Phone Number",class: "phone" %>

				      <%= f.submit "Start Your Story", class: "pure-button" %>
				    <% end %>
			
				</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="content-wrapper">
		<div class="content-head is-center"><a name="about">More About StoryTime</a></div>
		<div class="content-body is-center">
		StoryTime sends parents nightly text messages of bedtime stories and related activities for face-to-face fun and learning.<br> Share a better just-before-bedtime.
		</div>
		<div class="pure-g">
			<div class="1-box pure-u-1-3">
				<h4 class="content-subhead">Put in Your Number</h4>
				<p>Cell phones are the most democratic form of technology. More people can be affected through the use of simple SMS.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="1-box pure-u-1-3">
				<h4 class="content-subhead">Get a Bedtime Story</h4>
				<p>A short, 160-character story ranging from the poems of Shel Silverstein to short chapter stories over the course of a few days.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="1-box pure-u-1-3">
				<h4 class="content-subhead">Play the Activities</h4>
				<p>Each story is accompanied by an activity based on the child's age. Let the story expand beyond the SMS.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="content-head is-center"><a name="contact">Contact Us</a></div>
		<div class="content-body is-center">
		Want to get involved? Send us an e-mail at storytime@example.com and we'll send you information about how you can help.
		</div>

	</div>
</center>


